snippet.title: TVaria SailorPeace
snippet.description:
IF YOU ARE UNDER 13, PLEASE LEAVE THIS CHANNEL IMMEDIATELY.

How's it going everyone? I am TVaria SailorPeace, but you may call me Candy or Candace. :) I normally do a lot of video editing...but lately, I have found myself voice acting a lot, especially in the Undertale and Sonic universes. I plan to keep on going since you guys seem to enjoy it. :)
If you wanna use any of the audio from my videos, feel free to do so, but make sure to give me credit. Don't forget to share with me! I wanna see them too!

Oh, and one other thing, please leave all gems you need at home. Rouge the Bat has been using my channel for her own videos as of late with her friends, frienemies, foes, and boyfriend. Don't let her see those gems.
